k on this doodle with my collaborators &ndash; Corrie Scalisi, Kevin Laughlin, Manuel Cl&eacute;ment, and Leon Hong.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>Posted by Sophia Foster-Dimino, Doodler</em></p>\r\n", "width": 600, "height": 200, "is_global": true, "is_highlighted": false, "is_dynamic": true, "standalone_html": "/logos/2013/hitchhikers.html", "youtube_id": "", "translations": {"ro": {"hover_text": "61 de ani de la na\u0219terea lui Douglas Adams", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "lt": {"hover_text": "Daglaso Adamso 61-asis gimtadienis", "query": "Daglasas Adamsas", "share_text": ""}, "lv": {"hover_text": "Duglasa Adamsa 61. dzim\u0161anas diena", "query": "Duglass Adamss", "share_text": ""}, "pl": {"hover_text": "Douglas Adams - 61. rocznica urodzin", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "tr": {"hover_text": "Douglas Adams'\u0131n 61'inci Do\u011fumg\u00fcn\u00fc", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "vi": {"hover_text": null, "query": null, "share_text": ""}, "ro-MD": {"hover_text": "61 de ani de la na\u0219terea lui Douglas Adams", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "en": {"hover_text": "Douglas Adams' 61st Birthday", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "pt-BR": {"hover_text": "61\u00ba Anivers\u00e1rio de Douglas Adams", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "no": {"hover_text": "Douglas Adams 61. f\u00f8dselsdag", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "nn": {"hover_text": "Douglas Adams 61. f\u00f8dselsdag", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "zh-TW": {"hover_text": "\u300a\u9280\u6cb3\u4fbf\u8eca\u6307\u5357\u300b\u4f5c\u8005\u3001\u82f1\u570b\u4f5c\u5bb6 Douglas Adams 61\u6b72\u8a95\u8fb0", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "nl": {"hover_text": "61e Geboortedag Douglas Adams", "query": "Douglas Adams", "share_text": ""}, "ru": {"hover_text": "61 \u0433\u043e\u0434 \u0441\u043e \u0434\u043d\u044f \u0440\u043e\u0436\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u0414\u0443\u0433\u043b\u0430\u0441\u04